Class ConfigReader

java.lang.Object
  com.rrs.corona.solutionsacceleratorstudio.messagehandler.ConfigReader

public class ConfigReader
extends java.lang.Object

This class reads the hotwirestudio.config file to get the initial parameters for starting the Composite Event Manager. All the required parameters are defined in this file.
